告：即使减产也不会接受对俄石油限价令 - 中新网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-cc93e58031c407c96331a36b2bb63a2b_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "53 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/570416284"}}, "attached_info": "ClQI/43foaKOwJlaEAMaCDg5MDQxNTA3IPWBtZwGMAA4D0Alcgk1NzA0MTYyODR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "38_1670238155.4639642", "card_id": "Q_570433835", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 14}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "在岸人民币兑美元汇率升破 1:7，人民币还会继续强势升值吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "人民币很强势，但是明年的中美货币利息，估计有 4% 以上的息差，这情况支持人民币继续强势升值吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-46f1215592d3a01fcb87d3b9ffd61cc5_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "53 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/570433835"}}, "attached_info": "ClQI/43foaKOwJlaEAMaCDg5MDQ1NDAwINPCtZwGMAA4FEAmcgk1NzA0MzM4MzV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "39_1670238155.4647171", "card_id": "Q_567250472", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 37}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你家周边的哪些地方，是你每年都想去拜访的，背后有什么故事？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "女朋友每每工作不顺利就去普陀寺..."}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-14706123f384a00ea9606c427ee0df57_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "53 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/567250472"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I/43foaKOwJlaEAMaCDg4MzM4MDk5IImh2JsGMAA4OkAncgk1NjcyNTA0NzJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}